longBusinessSummary: Enviro-Serv, Inc. provides property maintenance services in the United States. It offers lawn/landscape maintenance and pest control services. The company was formerly known as Transfer Technology International Corp. and changed its name to Enviro-Serv, Inc. in March 2013 to reflect its new strategic corporate direction. Enviro-Serv, Inc. is based in Tampa, Florida.
